WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:02.000
I'm an artist.

00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:05.880
Being an artist
is the greatest job there is.

00:00:06.760 --> 00:00:09.056
And I really pity
each and every one of you

00:00:09.080 --> 00:00:11.776
who has to spend your days
discovering new galaxies

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:14.456
or saving humanity from global warming.

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:16.936
(Laughter)

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:19.880
But being an artist
is also a daunting job.

00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:24.480
I spend every day,
from nine to six, doing this.

